svg.title: EuiComboBox selectors quick reference
svg.desc: EuiComboBox provides five selectors for its inner elements: [data-test-subj="euiComboBoxPill"] for selected options, [data-test-subj="comboBoxSearchInput"] for the search input field, [data-test-subj="comboBoxClearButton"] for the clear button, [role="option"] for the list options, and [role="option"][aria-selected="true"] for the selected list options
